  "text": "The low number of PhalNLP pseudogenes is remarkable compared to the situation in the Hy. arabidopsidis genome where 14 HaNLP genes and 15 HaNLP pseudogenes were identified [CITATION_1] , and in the Phytophthora sojae genome where 33 PsNLP genes and 37 PsNLP pseudogenes were identified [CITATION_2] . In Pl. halstedii 19 PhalNLP genes were identified, yet only one PhalNLP pseudogene (Additional file 2: Figure S15) ; the latter has a premature stop codon when compared to its most closely related PhalNLP gene PHALS_14423 (Additional file 2: Figure S16 ).",
